        <h2>4. Subscription Plans & Billing</h2>
        <p><strong>Plan Tiers:</strong> Zipply offers three subscription levels:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Normal (Free):</strong> 3 short URLs + 2 QR codes per day, forever free</li>
          <li><strong>Pro:</strong> Rs 199/month for 10 short URLs + 10 QR codes per day</li>
          <li><strong>Plus:</strong> Rs 299/month for 25 short URLs + 25 QR codes per day</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Daily Limits:</strong> Usage limits reset daily at midnight IST (Asia/Kolkata timezone). Once exhausted, you cannot create new links or QR codes until the next day.</p>
        <p><strong>Subscription Validity:</strong> Paid plans are valid for exactly 30 days from activation. After expiry, your account automatically reverts to the Normal (Free) plan.</p>
        <p><strong>Plan Changes:</strong> You may upgrade to a higher tier anytime. Downgrading or changing plans is only possible after your current plan expires.</p>
        <p><strong>Payments:</strong> All payments are processed through Razorpay in test mode. By upgrading, you authorize payment and agree to Razorpay's terms.</p>
        <p><strong>No Refunds:</strong> Subscription fees are non-refundable. Cancellations take effect at plan expiry.</p>

