        <p><strong>Expiry:</strong> URLs can have optional expiry dates. After expiry, the short link no longer redirects. Deletion is immediate upon your request.</p>
        <p><strong>Deletion:</strong> When you delete a shortened URL or QR code, it is immediately disabled and cannot be recovered. Links created by others using your custom IDs remain active unless individually deleted.</p>
        <p><strong>Link Removal:</strong> Zipply reserves the right to remove or disable any links that contain illegal, harmful, or abusive content.</p>

